Kužiš kako bas gitara

00:37:29.270 --> 00:37:31.034
i bas bubanj
drže isti ritam?

00:37:31.190 --> 00:37:32.555
Sad ćeš čuti, čekaj.

00:37:32.670 --> 00:37:34.434
Lijepo sam vam rekao,
tebi posebno,

00:37:34.550 --> 00:37:36.279
da prestanete kenjat na krevet.

00:37:36.390 --> 00:37:37.880
Ne možeš stavit' zeca na krevet

00:37:38.030 --> 00:37:39.555
i onda očekivat' da se
ne pokenja na njega.

00:37:39.670 --> 00:37:41.114
Ovakav akord...

00:37:41.229 --> 00:37:42.310
Daa.

00:37:43.869 --> 00:37:44.916
Ovako nešto...

00:37:45.029 --> 00:37:46.599
<i>Da, da, da, da, da, milje</i>

00:37:46.709 --> 00:37:49.155
<i>Milje ispod mene...</i>

00:37:49.269 --> 00:37:52.079
<i>Na putu prema zvijezdama
pokazala mi je...</i>

00:37:52.189 --> 00:37:54.077
<i>Ulicu Dame,
Georgeovu ulicu</i>

00:37:54.188 --> 00:37:56.077
<i>Milje ispod mene...</i>

00:37:56.188 --> 00:37:58.111
- Ovo je dobro. Sviđa mi se.
