01:35:01.267 --> 01:35:02.597
Zašto?

01:35:02.706 --> 01:35:05.152
Pa, djedov čamac je i
dalje tamo na vezu.

01:35:05.266 --> 01:35:07.587
Otplovit ćemo u Englesku, nas dvoje.

01:35:07.706 --> 01:35:10.277
Sve smo sredili. Samo nam
treba prijevoz do luke.

01:35:10.386 --> 01:35:11.547
Da, naravno.

01:35:11.666 --> 01:35:13.031
Kad ste mislili krenuti?

01:35:13.146 --> 01:35:14.829
Sada.

01:35:14.945 --> 01:35:17.186
Sada?

01:35:17.305 --> 01:35:19.546
Znate li nekoga u Engleskoj?

01:35:19.705 --> 01:35:21.469
- Ne.
- Imate li što funti?

01:35:21.585 --> 01:35:23.349
Ne.

01:35:23.465 --> 01:35:25.627
- Ne?
- Ne.

01:35:26.744 --> 01:35:28.269
Ona ima svoje fotografije.

01:35:28.384 --> 01:35:31.274
Ja svoje spotove i demo - snimke.

01:35:32.824 --> 01:35:34.508
Idemo.
Da uzmem ključeve.

01:36:18.220 --> 01:36:21.508
Vidjet ćemo se, mama.

01:36:21.620 --> 01:36:23.224
Volim te.

01:37:05.736 --> 01:37:07.067
OK.

01:37:07.216 --> 01:37:08.706
Zovi čim stigneš tamo.

01:37:08.816 --> 01:37:10.625
- Bez zajebancije, može?
- Zvat ću.

01:37:10.736 --> 01:37:13.342
OK.

01:37:15.775 --> 01:37:18.779
Hej, prije nego kreneš...,

01:37:18.935 --> 01:37:22.576
imam tu neke tekstove za pjesme.

01:37:22.695 --> 01:37:24.140
- Stvarno?
- Da, malo je

01:37:24.255 --> 01:37:25.541
tok svijesti

01:37:25.695 --> 01:37:27.220
ali je o klincu i curi.

01:37:27.334 --> 01:37:28.495
U budućnosti.

01:37:28.654 --> 01:37:30.656
- Dodaj malo glazbe tome kad stigneš.
- OK.

01:37:30.774 --> 01:37:32.856
Da sam bar ja to napravio.

01:37:34.494 --> 01:37:35.734
Vjerojatno ćeš poginuti.

01:37:35.854 --> 01:37:36.821
Ali svejedno, kreni.

01:37:39.693 --> 01:37:41.343
Moraš nas posjetiti.

01:37:41.453 --> 01:37:42.943
Izgledaš malo ludo.

01:37:43.053 --> 01:37:44.464
OK.

01:37:44.573 --> 01:37:45.904
Pazi mi na brata.

01:37:46.013 --> 01:37:47.174
Bit će izgubljen bez mene.

01:37:47.293 --> 01:37:49.864
Hoću.

01:38:13.251 --> 01:38:14.776
Zovem te kasnije.

01:38:14.891 --> 01:38:16.221
Može. Kreni.

01:38:16.330 --> 01:38:18.014
Odavde.

01:38:18.130 --> 01:38:19.541
Dobro, moramo krenuti

01:38:19.650 --> 01:38:20.811
oko onog otočića pa ravno.

01:38:20.930 --> 01:38:21.817
Ravno za Wales.

01:38:21.930 --> 01:38:23.136
OK. Ravno naprijed.

01:39:15.806 --> 01:39:18.615
To! To!

01:39:55.722 --> 01:39:58.202
Sad ćeš malo sjesti dolje.

01:40:00.122 --> 01:40:01.453
Zašto?

01:40:03.762 --> 01:40:06.002
Eto zato.

01:40:12.361 --> 01:40:13.726
O, Bože.

01:40:13.841 --> 01:40:14.967
Jesi dobro?

01:40:15.081 --> 01:40:16.890
Da.

01:40:17.001 --> 01:40:18.047
Jesi ti dobro?

01:40:18.160 --> 01:40:19.650
Jesam.

01:40:19.760 --> 01:40:20.921
Conor!

01:40:23.560 --> 01:40:24.447
Isuse!

01:40:32.080 --> 01:40:33.411
O, bože.

